node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Brian Bosché @brianbosche When was 25 I thought I had made it after got married and found my dream job. But a week into my new job my whole life changed. Here is what happened...'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2 Brian Bosché @brianbosche Society told me to go to school, get the degree, the internship, the job and get married. So I listened...'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Brian Bosché @brianbosche went to law school, got my degree, got married, and got my dream job as a national journalist I packed with my wife and moved to Ohio to pursue my dream. thought had made it.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Brian Bosché @brianbosche But a week into my new job my wife left me... And 10 months later my position was eliminated. The same month my divorce was final.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Brian Bosché @brianbosche Everything on me. worked for turned My perfect job, my relationship, and my entire identity wiped out.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Brian Bosché @brianbosche I was sitting in my apartment, out of money and options and was wondering what was next for me. I felt so unwanted and unqualified...'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Brian Bosché @brianbosche I had to take a sales job. remember a conversation with a woman who told me: "I can't buy from you, don't even know my purpose!" I told her: "I don't know mine either." So I asked myself, If finding purpose was so important shouldn't there be a process?'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Brian Bosché @brianbosche I spent the next 6 years researching purpose and created a process to hel pother people find their purpose. We're told to "follow our passion" and "try a bunch of things" but that's the worst advice ever...'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Brian Bosché @brianbosche Without knowing WHO you are and WHO you're helping you'l just waste years jumping from one idea to another wondering what's next to you.'.

Photo shared by Business & Entrepreneur on September 11, 2021 tagging @brianandgab. May be an image of text that says 'Brian Bosché @brianbosche I started helping other people find their purpose and become happier employees, authors, entrepreneurs, speakers... Once you find and apply your purpose nothing can stop you from becoming successful. If you'd like to find YOUR true calling, DM me "PURPOSE"!'.
Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3-5 years of sacrifice, saving, focus, ano investing can set you up for the rest of your life.'.
